Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.76,0:00:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將這片寂靜撕裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.34,0:00:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引領整個世界\N來到熾熱之焰的最深處吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.71,0:00:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神Zwei
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.05,0:00:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的誓言\N灌注在朝天高舉的憤怒之拳中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.76,0:00:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再度點燃你的熱情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.13,0:00:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解放那沸騰不已的火紅熱血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.84,0:00:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰都已無法阻止你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.81,0:00:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓一片黑暗的明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.65,0:00:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,燃起希望的光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.02,0:01:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,化作捍衛弱者的獠牙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.46,0:01:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烈陽超重爆炎霸!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.89,0:01:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫無畏懼的向前奔馳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.87,0:01:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到衝過那深紅色的終點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.07,0:01:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在最後一刻燃盡一切吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.51,0:01:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.53,0:01:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守護著世界和平的正義秘密結社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.27,0:01:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓諸位都能見到明日的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.34,0:01:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類的夥伴、愛與真實的友方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.40,0:01:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到地球戰騎隊網站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.41,0:01:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是負責引導各位的愛娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.11,0:01:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還請各位多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.58,0:02:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於想瀏覽的頁面\N請從這邊的選項選取
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.92,0:02:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉\N本網頁目前還在製作中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.76,0:02:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉\N本網頁目前還在製作中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.39,0:02:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉...\N這算什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.36,0:02:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部都還在製作中嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.33,0:02:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真是粗糙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.90,0:02:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是英司的惡作劇呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.84,0:02:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.67,0:02:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是地圖吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.34,0:02:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想是啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.21,0:02:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直和小鬼的塗鴉一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.75,0:02:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真像英司會做的事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.45,0:02:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「華麗的再會」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.72,0:02:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂~真的是這個方向嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.16,0:02:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是照這地圖走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.49,0:02:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方向應該沒錯才對呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.33,0:02:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們都走了好久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.16,0:02:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧我們該不會迷路了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.33,0:02:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就只有一條路耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.57,0:02:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之也只有繼續走了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.25,0:03:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,入侵者?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.75,0:03:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的在23區共計四人\N目前正以C程序應對中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.68,0:03:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把畫面轉到螢幕上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.15,0:03:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.29,0:03:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是一般百姓\N即刻開始查對身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.96,0:03:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以不用調查了\N我認得這群孩子們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.30,0:03:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至此集團會議可以結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.86,0:03:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位辛苦妳們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.67,0:03:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生\N保安部有狀況向您報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.61,0:03:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.04,0:03:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的有訪客光臨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.08,0:03:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,訪客?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.01,0:03:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,累死我了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.15,0:03:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家再也走不動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.99,0:03:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.29,0:03:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該早就穿過森林了才對呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.32,0:03:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到處都看不到像出口的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.09,0:03:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是徹底迷路了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.70,0:03:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦...真的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.20,0:04:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一個騎著馬的男人\N和一個騎著馬的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.21,0:04:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那位女僕姊姊耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.27,0:04:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳認得她嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.84,0:04:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是英司住的城堡裡的女僕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.68,0:04:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是上次在地下室\N救了小弓的大姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.68,0:04:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.96,0:04:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...我們是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.96,0:04:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,諸位是英司的朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.06,0:04:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是葛萊因.桑德曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.57,0:04:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎蒞臨聖日耳曼城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.54,0:04:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.11,0:04:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我上次沒能向妳道謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.21,0:04:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳救了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.48,0:04:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不用客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.25,0:04:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.45,0:04:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在看起來很有精神呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.15,0:04:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.26,0:04:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以看到城門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.76,0:04:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們馬上就要到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.80,0:05:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好壯觀喔~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.07,0:05:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好華麗的城堡哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.67,0:05:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大的城堡喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.47,0:05:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,形狀也很稀奇呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.28,0:05:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司他就在這裡面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.12,0:05:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撐不下去了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.12,0:05:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是有夠沒出息的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.22,0:05:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家也...快要不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.76,0:05:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為外星異種\N又再度開始行動了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.16,0:05:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們這裡的"鬼"也就跟著復活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.77,0:05:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,訪客?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.17,0:05:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒有這樣的預定才對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.34,0:05:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N似乎是來拜訪英司少爺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.41,0:05:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.91,0:05:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後30秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.69,0:06:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.50,0:06:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位是英司少爺的朋友嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.43,0:06:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的我們是高中同班同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.30,0:06:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同班同學?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.87,0:06:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.94,0:06:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.17,0:06:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小弓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.74,0:06:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.64,0:06:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.08,0:06:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.31,0:06:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看來挺好的嘛英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.12,0:06:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小香大鳥高須...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.79,0:06:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你們會在這兒啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.29,0:06:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂愛娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.09,0:06:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的琉菜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.16,0:06:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那丫頭...\N為什麼和斗牙這麼親熱呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.60,0:06:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.13,0:06:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們是英司少爺的朋友而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露妹妹好久不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.20,0:06:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.47,0:06:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅羅多看起來也不錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.88,0:07:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是在做什麼英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.82,0:07:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打算把這座城\N變成觀光景點是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.45,0:07:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼辦法嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.92,0:07:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家就是一肚子鳥氣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.45,0:07:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛超重神賭命戰鬥的\N明明就是我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.76,0:07:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻被當成EFA的功勞了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.39,0:07:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.83,0:07:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是自外星異種手下\N保護這星球上的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.23,0:07:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別人到底怎麼想並不是重點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.70,0:07:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我們戰敗的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.30,0:07:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這星球的生命也將滅絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.61,0:07:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.84,0:07:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們來這裡是不是會讓英司...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.21,0:07:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別在意啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.41,0:07:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他本來就常常被罵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.35,0:07:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.02,0:07:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在擔心英司?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.79,0:07:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並不是妳想的那樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.99,0:07:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.33,0:07:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜引導貴賓們參觀城內吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.60,0:07:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.30,0:07:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就開始\N為各位介紹聖日耳曼城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.64,0:07:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.57,0:08:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位有什麼特別想看的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.18,0:08:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司也有駕駛對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.68,0:08:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家想要去看看女僕們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.38,0:08:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯我也想看女僕\N超重神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.99,0:08:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.35,0:08:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就從\N超重機組機庫開始介紹起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.03,0:08:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些飛機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.20,0:08:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會在合神後\N會變成超重神的雙腳組件吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.50,0:08:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的那是G攻擊機與G打擊機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.27,0:08:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司他開的就是這個嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.71,0:08:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的是由英司少爺\N駕駛這架G攻擊機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.11,0:08:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月小姐駕駛另一架G打擊機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.55,0:08:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來與外星異種進行作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.58,0:08:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司他還真的是在保衛地球呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.79,0:08:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.65,0:08:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有下面的電鑽戰車呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.99,0:08:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好...好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.22,0:08:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那輛叫作G鑽機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.16,0:08:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是琉菜小姐與我駕駛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.13,0:08:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也有駕駛呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.66,0:08:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N不過我還不太能進入狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.90,0:08:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦~妳好厲害喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.00,0:09:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害對吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.77,0:09:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜姊可是我們女僕的代表呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.81,0:09:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒真是太棒了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.58,0:09:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種不採用螺旋造型的鑽頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.91,0:09:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人能感受到那份堅持之美啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.08,0:09:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小哥你的嗜好挺不錯的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.29,0:09:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天氣真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.66,0:09:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的貴賓是英司少爺的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.36,0:09:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家可要打起精神來烹調啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.23,0:09:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.37,0:09:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊桑德曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.17,0:09:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的是超重壓力拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.67,0:09:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛拳! 飛拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.18,0:09:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帥斃了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.71,0:09:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然超級機器人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.28,0:09:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不把拳頭打出去\N感覺就不夠熱血了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.15,0:09:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的是光線技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.69,0:09:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要開始囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.29,0:09:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光線! 光線!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.86,0:09:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.26,0:10:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朵莉雅只要一熱衷起來\N就完全不顧周遭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.73,0:10:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這點高須也半斤八兩啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.57,0:10:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿他沒辦法呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.90,0:10:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我將為各位介紹司令室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.44,0:10:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司令室是作什麼的地方啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.94,0:10:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.31,0:10:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以稱作這個城的頭腦的地方...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.15,0:10:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.62,0:10:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜前去野餐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.52,0:10:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,野餐...是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.76,0:10:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,野餐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.53,0:10:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.49,0:10:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上要開始歡迎貴賓的野餐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.43,0:10:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會很快樂的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.64,0:10:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼超重戰騎的諸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.87,0:10:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向野餐出發吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.89,0:11:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的都來野餐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.96,0:11:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼還得開著超重機組來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.70,0:11:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.00,0:11:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在外星異種恢復活動的此刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.54,0:11:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時時做好準備\N是我們地球戰騎隊的義務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.14,0:11:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好一板一眼喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.88,0:11:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位讓大家久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.35,0:11:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,諸君手邊都有飲料了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.92,0:11:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.22,0:11:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天就不用拘泥小節了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.62,0:11:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盡情享受吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.52,0:11:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.79,0:11:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.90,0:11:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說這個女人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.14,0:11:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對就是英司少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.91,0:11:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是他頭一次來城裡的打扮嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.84,0:11:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦~還挺適合他的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.65,0:12:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋! 我那是逼不得已的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.08,0:12:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎唷那你偷窺女僕們更衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.22,0:12:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是逼不得已的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.52,0:12:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊~對了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.13,0:12:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我洗澡的時候也被英司偷窺過!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.10,0:12:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.33,0:12:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司你好下流喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.03,0:12:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好下流哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.23,0:12:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司你好下流是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.77,0:12:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.90,0:12:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這很理所當然的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.94,0:12:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你是個年青小伙子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.87,0:12:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像那一晚也是...對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.08,0:12:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一晚?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.94,0:12:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...我們什麼都沒有做!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.18,0:12:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對啦\N哪有人會把英司當回事嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.82,0:12:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.79,0:12:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我等一下\N剛剛那句話是什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.89,0:12:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蝶雪拉、瑪莉妮雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月小姐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.56,0:12:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起喝啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.37,0:12:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷~文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.40,0:12:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛和兩個小妹妹\N靜靜窩在一邊呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.40,0:12:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧~你也給我喝啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.57,0:13:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是說\N你沒辦法把成熟女人當對象呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.61,0:13:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳喝醉了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.61,0:13:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀?你身上挺香的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.21,0:13:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這味道怎麼這麼讓我懷念呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.38,0:13:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有很多喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.72,0:13:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請別客氣盡情的喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.46,0:13:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.96,0:13:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是覺得你過的真好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.13,0:13:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.53,0:13:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.07,0:13:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小弓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.24,0:13:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你見到綾香姊了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.87,0:13:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒見到老姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她還是一樣的消失中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.44,0:13:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.65,0:13:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.85,0:13:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼消失了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.68,0:13:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有在找她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.79,0:13:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但怎麼找...怎麼找...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.39,0:13:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一樣哪裡都...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.96,0:13:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找不到啦~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.16,0:13:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人擔心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.97,0:13:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.04,0:14:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦~羅羅多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.21,0:14:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪白的野生者呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.74,0:14:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解放你身上蘊藏的野生之力\N實現我等的心願...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.08,0:14:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去把綾香找出來吧!\N白色之獸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.47,0:14:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅羅多...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.04,0:14:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家好像都很盡興的樣子嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.07,0:14:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舉辦這次的野餐真是沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.54,0:14:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很盡興的樣子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.08,0:14:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.98,0:14:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很高興嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.35,0:14:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊大家都很高興嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.49,0:14:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在沖繩一定很好玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.26,0:14:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定很好玩才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.39,0:15:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像真的很好玩喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.10,0:15:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們三位\N看起來並不是很高興嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.23,0:15:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的桑德曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.27,0:15:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們很高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.61,0:15:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?那就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.37,0:15:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的! 我們好的很
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.68,0:15:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是很對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.75,0:15:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然麻煩客人做這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.55,0:15:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,零嘴也要全部拿來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.99,0:15:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.49,0:15:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小香發生什麼了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.39,0:15:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好像壓到什麼了耶...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.03,0:15:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說壓到什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.34,0:15:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.71,0:15:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追上去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.61,0:15:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擠死人了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.51,0:15:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們兩個\N幹嘛全塞到我這裡啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.22,0:15:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起因為情況緊急就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.32,0:15:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就忍著點嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.79,0:16:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是再不快找到她們的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.92,0:16:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露那邊情況如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.62,0:16:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有...我這裡也沒看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.99,0:16:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現G鑽機機體尚無損傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.33,0:16:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確認駕駛艙內有兩個生命反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.67,0:16:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人皆平安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.80,0:16:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙快點停住它啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.70,0:16:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有用\N對方不接受超重皇下的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.07,0:16:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我將繼續追蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.91,0:16:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.44,0:16:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上去和你會合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.31,0:16:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家跟我來唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.25,0:16:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爺請您快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.12,0:16:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你快跟上啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.59,0:16:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅羅多...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.35,0:16:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是很中意那裡呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.02,0:16:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼都停不下來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.73,0:16:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朵莉雅為什麼停不住它呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.86,0:16:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是個人鎖定在運作中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.83,0:16:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以一切指命都不被接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.40,0:16:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想停住它\N只能先用萬用鑰匙重開機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.10,0:16:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再進行合神才行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.54,0:16:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬用鑰匙呢?\N妳想我會帶它來野餐嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.44,0:16:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是喔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.08,0:16:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朵莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.21,0:16:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要重開機就行了是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.65,0:17:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.25,0:17:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是...是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.42,0:17:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣的話\N必須直接與G鑽機接觸才...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.59,0:17:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我進去裡面進行重開機吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.62,0:17:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各超重機組準備合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.49,0:17:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在G鑽機重開的同時進行合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.33,0:17:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.90,0:17:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們上吧彈劾號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.88,0:17:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩位妳們沒受傷吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.81,0:17:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.32,0:17:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的我們沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.98,0:17:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.63,0:17:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重戰騎的諸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.60,0:17:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啟動合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.00,0:17:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工學型態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.97,0:18:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.05,0:19:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.75,0:19:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.62,0:19:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位你們沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.49,0:19:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯我們沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.96,0:19:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是兩位有了什麼萬一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.13,0:20:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家...人家...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.43,0:20:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了她們都沒事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.56,0:20:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笑一個吧愛娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.86,0:20:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊對啊笑一個嘛愛娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.34,0:20:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.34,0:20:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是我害妳們\N遇到這麼恐怖的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.01,0:20:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是呀媚月小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.78,0:20:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然還在G鑽機裡堆酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.95,0:20:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.31,0:20:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.12,0:20:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...好想吐喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.62,0:20:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過大家都沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.99,0:20:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.56,0:20:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀太好了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.62,0:20:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.09,0:20:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.53,0:20:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.40,0:20:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙你腦袋上的是羅羅多吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.50,0:20:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠為什麼會在那裡啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.10,0:20:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是很中意那裡呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.95,0:21:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生...是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.29,0:21:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是這個服裝...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.19,0:21:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也罷挺像那男人會有的造型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.63,0:21:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.80,0:21:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這張肖像畫\N是在18世紀時所繪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.60,0:21:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,18世紀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.24,0:21:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N肖像上的人是聖日耳曼伯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.14,0:21:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是法國貴族也是鍊金術士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.94,0:21:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在當時又被稱為時間的旅行者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.01,0:21:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鍊金術士和時間的旅行者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.55,0:21:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聖日耳曼伯爵...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.95,0:21:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是有意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.99,0:21:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再去做更深入的調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.13,0:21:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.57,0:21:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想...休息喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.31,0:21:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因熱戀而無法成眠的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.58,0:22:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經看膩了星座占卜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.89,0:22:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為想要聽到人的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.06,0:22:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以隨意打了電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.39,0:22:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了靠不住的語音留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.90,0:22:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在到底在哪裡呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.94,0:22:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,映著冰箱內的燈光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.17,0:22:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在狹小的宇宙裡彷徨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.74,0:22:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我的唱片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.98,0:22:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唱針已經跳開不知幾次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.19,0:22:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我相信這不變的溫度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.46,0:22:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直到什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.56,0:22:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OHBABY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.13,0:22:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳邊輕語嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.56,0:22:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對讓我聽聽你溫柔的聲音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.07,0:22:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們手牽手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.10,0:23:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同被沁入你心中的\N淺淺呼吸籠罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.31,0:23:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳邊輕語嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.68,0:23:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對讓我聽聽你溫柔的聲音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.19,0:23:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們閉上雙眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.15,0:23:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同在溜進你夢裡的\N甜美節奏中融化吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.77,0:23:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們因為慰勞旅行\N所以要去泡溫泉了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.84,0:23:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是感謝桑德曼先生\N太感謝他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.97,0:23:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是高興的時候啦\N裘依露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.34,0:23:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看外星異種又...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.31,0:23:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此外\N好像還有群身份不明的人士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.15,0:23:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在注意著我們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.12,0:23:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是斗牙少爺的朋友嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.32,0:23:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回\N「熱鬥!愚裸美溫泉!!」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.86,0:23:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回我們也將照料各位的和平哦